            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Not a manual penalty in most cases, but thin content triggers algorithmic suppression. Google's Panda algorithm and the Helpful Content system both reduce the visibility of sites with significant proportions of thin, low-value content — a sitewide effect, not just page-level.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
